---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<BaseHead title={`Our Story | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
</head>

<body>
	<Header />

	<main>
		<section class="content">
		<h1>Our Story</h1>

		<p>
			Sonoran Rise Bakery was born from a simple belief:
			<strong>good bread is worth making well.</strong>
		</p>

		<p>
			In a world that often values speed and convenience, we chose a different
			path—one that embraces patience, craftsmanship, and a deep respect for the
			ingredients that make great bread possible.
		</p>

		<p>
			What began as a fascination with baking gradually became a passion for
			understanding grain itself. Learning about heritage wheats, flour milling,
			fermentation, and the people who dedicate their lives to preserving these
			traditions revealed that every loaf has a story long before it reaches the
			oven.
		</p>

		<hr>

		<h2>Inspired by the Sonoran Desert</h2>

		<p>
			Our name reflects the place that inspired so much of this journey.
		</p>

		<p>
			The Sonoran Desert is often misunderstood. At first glance it appears harsh
			and unforgiving, yet those who spend time paying attention discover a place
			filled with remarkable beauty, resilience, and life.
		</p>

		<p>
			Much like artisan bread, its character reveals itself to those willing to
			slow down.
		</p>

		<p>
			From the colors of desert sunsets to the brief bloom of spring wildflowers,
			the Sonoran Desert reminds us that patience often rewards us with something
			extraordinary.
		</p>

		<hr>

		<h2>Our Purpose</h2>

		<p>
			We hope every loaf we bake encourages people to gather around a table,
			share a meal, and enjoy simple moments that are too often overlooked.
		</p>

		<p>
			Bread has nourished families and communities for thousands of years. We are
			honored to continue that tradition with every loaf that leaves our oven.
		</p>

		<hr>

		<h2>Looking Ahead</h2>

		<p>
			Sonoran Rise Bakery is more than a place to buy bread. It is an ongoing
			journey of learning, improving, and exploring the remarkable world of grain.
		</p>

		<p>
			We are committed to continually refining our craft, supporting exceptional
			farmers and millers, and sharing what we learn along the way.
		</p>

		<p>
			We believe the best bread tells a story—not only of flour, water, salt, and
			time, but also of the people, places, and traditions that made it possible.
		</p>

		<p>
			Thank you for being part of ours.
		</p>
		</section>
	</main>

	<Footer />
</body>
</html>